<div class="title">A Fairly Nasty Ride</div>
<div class="substance">Bupropion (Wellbutrin) & Amphetamine (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=6&Exact=1">6</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; 6. "A Fairly Nasty Ride: An Experience with Bupropion (Wellbutrin) & Amphetamine (Adderall) (exp16856)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 16, 2002. erowid.org/exp/16856</div>

